---

<PageLayout page="membership">
  <Container class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:gap-12 py-14">
    <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-light text-center">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut quis ipsum et
      neque viverra pulvinar sit amet quis sem. Orci varius natoque penatibus et
      magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Etiam sit amet urna
      viverra, laoreet dolor nec, elementum nisi. Morbi dapibus et justo a
      facilisis.
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://bookwhen.com/flicktt/memberships"
      target="_blank"
      class="m-auto"
    >
      <Button size="lg">Become a member</Button>
    </a>
  </Container>
  <PointsRow pointConfig={pointConfig} />
  <Container class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:gap-12 py-14">
    <SplitLayoutContainer>
      <SplitLayoutLeft title="Membership benefits" />
      <SplitLayoutRight>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
          <PricingCard title="Normal" prices={pricingConfig.normal} bg="dark" />
          <PricingCard
            title="Members"
            prices={pricingConfig.members}
            bg="yellow"
          />
        </div>
      </SplitLayoutRight>
    </SplitLayoutContainer>
  </Container>
  <Faqs faqConfig={faqConfig} />
</PageLayout>
